parameters:
Thief Nora: I think this is the entrance, but... it's mostly
buried.

Priestess Sophia: We can also search for another hidden
passage, you know~ (glancing)
Clea: We don't have much time (glancing)
Mage Relm: W-What is it!? Are you telling me to go?

Mage Relm: Absolutely not! Besides, we don't even know where
it leads to--

Thief Nora: Please, Relm-san! It's possible that the Emma
Thief Guild is also involved!

Thief Nora: If the Imperial Army starts moving in earnest,
my comrades... everyone will be killed.
Mage Relm: I understand, I'll do it!

Mage Relm: I'm doing this hole-digging because it's a
request from my friend, the great genius! Isn't that nice!

Clea: We will be waiting here. If you determine that it's
dangerous, please come back immediately.

Priestess Sophia: Because it's important not to push
yourself too hard, Relm-chan sometimes tends to be reckless.

Mage Relm: Hehe, a true genius can do anything! There's no
reason why I can't do what thieves can do.
Mage Relm: Everyone, please wait here for the results!
